Start
/ A read of config.json lands the file as {object, json} (architect's
/ shape-based typing — keeps today's json→object). The critical lazy
/ invariant: stamping `type=object` does NOT parse — `%cfg%` untouched is
/ still the raw json *string*. Materialisation only fires on navigation
/ (see ReadConfigJson_NavigateMaterialisesField). Requires the config.json
/ fixture committed alongside.
- read file 'config.json', write to %cfg%
- assert %cfg.Type.Name% equals "object"
- assert %cfg.Type.Kind% equals "json"
- assert %cfg% equals "{\"port\":8080}"
